---
Source:
  Title: Breathe and Be - A Book of Mindfulness Poems
  By:
    Author: Kare Coombs
    Illustrator: Anna Emilia Laitinen
  Publisher: Sounds True
  Copyright: 2017
---
I breathe slowly in,
I breathe slowly out. My breath
is a river of peace.
I am here in the world.
Each moment I can breathe and be.
